<%--
button2.dsp

{{IS_NOTE
	Purpose:
		
	Description:
		In Safari, the shape of <button> is not pleasure, so we use
		<input> if no image is required
	History:
		Wed Aug  4 10:19:50     2008, Created by robbiecheng
}}IS_NOTE

